<p>One significant regulatory challenge Ripple faces is the classification of its native cryptocurrency, XRP, by regulatory bodies such as the SEC. Ripple has been actively engaged in ongoing discussions with regulators to clarify the legal status of XRP, providing regulatory certainty to market participants.</p>



