<p>Expanding its global reach through strategic alliances with major banking partners, Ripple&#8217;s partnerships have had a significant impact on its market penetration and currency liquidity. These collaborations have allowed Ripple to establish a strong presence in the financial industry and increase the adoption of its digital currency, XRP.</p>



