<h3 class="wp-block-heading">Collaborations with International Money Transfer Services</h3>



<p>Through partnerships with international money transfer services, Ripple has solidified its position in the remittance and payment service industry. These collaborations have allowed Ripple to leverage its digital asset, XRP, to facilitate faster and more cost-effective global payments.</p>



